2026-02-25 15:58:57 [DBG] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@p='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT s1."Id", s1."Content", s1."CorrectAnswerId", s1."Image", s0."Id", s0."AnswerIndex", s0."Content", s0."SpecialQuestionId"
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Content", s."CorrectAnswerId", s."Image", gen_random_uuid() AS c
    FROM "SpecialQuestions" AS s
    ORDER BY gen_random_uuid()
    LIMIT @p
) AS s1

SELECT s1."Id", s1."Content", s1."CorrectAnswerId", s1."Image", s0."Id", s0."AnswerIndex", s0."Content", s0."SpecialQuestionId"
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Content", s."CorrectAnswerId", s."Image", gen_random_uuid() AS c
    FROM "SpecialQuestions" AS s
    ORDER BY gen_random_uuid()
    LIMIT @p
) AS s1
LEFT JOIN "SpecialAnswers" AS s0 ON s1."Id" = s0."SpecialQuestionId"
ORDER BY s1.c, s1."Id"

    SELECT b."Id", b."Content", b."CorrectAnswerId", b."Image", gen_random_uuid() AS c
    FROM "BaseQuestions" AS b
    ORDER BY gen_random_uuid()
    LIMIT @p
) AS b1
LEFT JOIN "BaseAnswers" AS b0 ON b1."Id" = b0."BaseQuestionId"
ORDER BY b1.c, b1."Id"

SELECT b1."Id", b1."Content", b1."CorrectAnswerId", b1."Image", b0."Id", b0."AnswerIndex", b0."BaseQuestionId", b0."Content"
FROM (
    SELECT b."Id", b."Content", b."CorrectAnswerId", b."Image", gen_random_uuid() AS c
    FROM "BaseQuestions" AS b
